definitely not wanted by any user.\n2.) Such effect upon your users could significantly harm your overall reputation and customer loss.","weakness":{"id":74,"name":"UI Redressing (Clickjacking)"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":254262,"file_name":"Dangerous_ClickJacking_Yelp.flv","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/254/262/5ffbbae94d2a2f570665b51ba1a68315e8ee5cbf/Dangerous_ClickJacking_Yelp.flv?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Dangerous_ClickJacking_Yelp.flv%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Dangerous_ClickJacking_Yelp.flv\u0026response-content-type=video%2Fx-flv\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQVNLSD7KF%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T084911Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQC5FZYMlS628CuhZFIJ1HEIqBwicJ6%2F9T9I9aZbSbFgmgIhAJ26eDcBc%2FGOufGkolfwBYzM2AL8tenUBQZa3nypwcrYKrsFCPH%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgzmyPwoXegWzTVOZxUqjwV1tzF63HAWxG%2BJKbAXG6OMhV0ZEI%2FBWvCmPTjsJtzW6jVBf9zAJbEcswkXX%2FBooJBJjGjDO475kShGTOklWZ0h7A4HO61fFj%2BHCHd0Z7A%2FZRgS5ybfkHTv9ASDt66EK%2FqXjXnIdbKNl8uT2X5zlteCJz1VKn1tMsF493dVHnqakDr7%2BY%2BckcsIParimJPwWwbhRNawxqM2h7BCoyGIE2sifVKcN5NFNnSowlzGHdaC084eM6jIK0IiZTq1EbcVD%2F9eg0XWtO%2B%2FMCr%2Bjbmy0S3LkpbcyC47Rscb2LqeIQkz1DqnZed3Q7DaaYWqWEb8k%2Bd5Gb3FTOl%2F%2F4EBlVTdsiLIrgp%2FEA7ImgUfdQocm%2FadpNAPnQJIQ0bbJbzTUtoatTC7kTy8%2Bdm0Ilh%2BrHkWZUSIBcJ2yNUkJSNQsluF9x%2BbyAZWrqz31rfXXXLlB20VHtzAsVW68GMX8SYH756IFpnQiarlKJSL7gpirSlrz2KgVKZsVx%2F0dmlg8obJymx603RTjl14H9XB4UxK8pqIMRE82H1otZ%2F3Jr4SavIRmY8jMa2V%2FxyZ8g1iJKmga0jhoCQ%2BSmzKgpRl7%2BptlILw53GrVLGB1KHhy4SZxSdImqD71oK0cm7EQM1MjeCc5Slk8NwgSW5GmsMiFt6FOPkDRWcakJpQusJ%2BwHGUzSpnNsYuKNHjnLnuDoS5yY3Hy1swfBMy42EPkEmqUMFYFTx3BxW1S6Ox%2BZPY2meonZGqQj2fqF9FRacP708fABAPnxjZtOmF7YJhLBKQIbzY5dho3vxRE5Wyl%2FMlikH8%2BD3D079nUTktQtNF